inn1.comm: good length delivery swings away to beat the outside edge.
moves forward and defends to mid-on.
mistimes the drive to mid-off.
turns it around to long leg to get off the mark.
drifts down the leg side, off the pad the ball goes past the keeper to fine leg fence.
better line from Mortaza on the off stump, defended with the full face off the bat on the front foot to the off side.
punches to the off side.
good shot from Salman, turns it around behind square leg and the ball races to the fence for the first boundary.
left alone outside the off stump, too wide.
fuller and swinging in, driven to mid-on.
short delivery and sits up nicely for Butt, who hammers it in the gap through cover to the fence.
back of a length delivery angled across, lets it go through to Dhiman Ghosh.
driven to the off side.
back of a length delivery and Akmal defends with a straight bat to the off side.
opens the face off the bat and plays it wide of thirdman for couple of runs.
good line from Mortaza, defended to mid-on on the front foot.
driven back to the bowler, Mortaza gets his hand to the ball and stops it.
good tight line on the off stump from Mortaza, pushes to the off side.
appeal for lbw as the ball nips in from outside the off stump, Akmal was looking to  leave the ball outside the off stump, strikes the pad and the appeal is turned down as it is outside the line.
pushes to the off side.
fuller delivery on the legs, driven to mid-on.
turns it off his legs to fine leg for a single.
punches off the back foot to mid-off.
back of a length delivery defended to the off side.
width outside the off stump and Akmal goes hard at it and hits in the air over backward point  to the fence.
pushes to mid-on.
good firm push through covers to the deep.
slower delivery from Mortaza, pushes to the right of midwicket for a single.
good shot from Akmal, width for him and he slashes in the air over point to the fence.
this time on the pads and Akmal fails to get some bat on it, off the pad the ball goes to the onside.
caught! Back of a length delivery and moving away slightly, Akmal looks to  play it down but the ball takes the outside edge and through to Junaid Siddique at first slip.
mistimes the drive to mid-off.
too wide outside the off stump and Butt misses the cut shot, signaled a wide.
defended to mid-off.
works it through midwicket to the deep, Mahumudullah chases it to the ropes and fields it.
pushes to the onside and takes off for a single, Butt sends him back as the fielders converge on the ball.
plays away from his body, pushes to the off side.
digs in a short one and Younis Khan goes for the hook, gets some glove on it and the ball flies over the keeper to fine leg.
good shot from Butt, cuts it nicely through cover-point to the fence.
plays to cover straight to the fielder.
defends with the full face off the bat to the off side.
slower delivery pushed to mid-off.
moves forward and pushes to mid-off.
shot! Wonderful timing as Butt works it wide of mid-on and the ball races to the fence.
full delivery driven down the ground to mid-on.
punches off the back foot to extra cover.
clips it in the air in the air through midwicket to the fence.
down the leg side and Younis Khan nudges to fine leg for a single.
slower delivery and bit fuller, Butt moves forward and drives to the left of short cover and the ball races to the fence.
short ball and Butt mistimes the pull through square leg.
close to the off stump and Younis khan plays it down to thirdman.
punches to the off side.
way outside the off stump and Butt goes in the air over cover to the fence.
coming into Butt, who works to the short midwicket fielder with the angle.
short ball pulled around to the onside, the ball keeps low.
punches to point.
looks to drive through the off side, the ball goes of the inside half off the bat over the bowler to the deep.
another mistimed shot to the off side.
mistimes for the third time in the over, cut to the off side.
mistimes to the onside.
works it through midwicket for couple of runs.
again works it through midwicket, this time for a single.
plays it through the onside to midwicket.
the ball straightens and Butt pushes down the track to mid-off.
cracking shot from Butt, room for him and he cuts through cover-point to the fence.
beautiful shot once again, puts his right foot forward and drives in the gap wide of mid-off to the fence.
works it through square leg for a single.
mistimes the drive to cover.
moves forward and pushes to mid-off.
works it in front of square leg to the fielder.
spins in and Butt plays to mid-on.
works to the onside to mid-on.
turns it through the vacant midwicket to the deep, brings up his 50, raises his bat to the crowd and Younis Khan shakes his hand.
moves back and plays through cover to the sweeper for a single.
defended to the off side.
moves forward and defends to the off side.
slides down the leg side, off the pad to the onside.
sweeps behind square leg for a single.
swept well to deep-square leg for a single.
defended on the front foot to the off side.
plays it to deep-backward square leg for a single.
works it to short fine leg.
sweeps it to fine leg, Aftab runs around from deep-square leg to field the ball.
cuts well but can only get a single as it was well fielded by Junaid Siddique at backward point.
good sweep shot, plays it through square leg to the fence.
flicks it in the air past the fielder at midwicket to the deep.
dropped! Down the wicket and hits it in the air to mid-on, Mortaza makes a great effort diving to his right to take the catch but fails to hold onto the ball.
pushes in the gap through cover for a single.
defended on the front foot.
defended to the off side.
defended down the track.
swept well to deep-square leg for a single.
punches wide of mid-on for a single.
plays it down the track.
cuts it late to short thirdman.
moves forward and with the full face off the bat drives to long off.
tosses it wide outside the off stump and Butt stretches and drives along the ground to extra cover.
moves forward and works it wide of mid-on for a single.
drives it back down the track.
good shot from Butt, tosses it outside the off stump and Butt swings it high and over wide long on fence for maximum.
works it behind square leg for a single.
defended with a straight bat down the track.
goes with the turn and pushes square of the wicket on the off side.
plays it through cover to the deep.
plays it through the off side to the deep.
punches down the ground to long off.
gets a leading edge to the off side.
defends with a straight bat to mid-on.
drives well to the right of mid-off for couple of runs.
driven to the sweeper cover.
defended on the front foot to the off side.
sweeps it behind square leg to the deep.
defended to the off side.
cuts and misses.
works it behind square leg for a single.
moves forward and drives down the ground to long off.
moves forward and pushes through cover to the deep.
punches it down the ground to long on for a single.
turns it around to the onside.
defended to the off side.
turns it around to the onside.
drives down the ground to long off.
moves forward and drives down the ground to long off.
moves forward and pushes back to the bowler.
punches down the ground to long on.
moves forward and drives through covers to the sweeper.
sweeps behind square leg to the deep.
plays bit uppishly past the bowler to long on.
works it to the fielder at midwicket.
driven to the off side, Ashraful quickly to his left fields the ball.
down the wicket and slightly miscues it in the air over the fielder at long on and into the fence.
uses his feet and drives it down the ground to long off.
pushes to the onside, bowler quickly moves to his left to field it.
driven down the ground to long off.
moves forward and defends to the off side.
punches down the ground to long on.
plays it back to the bowler.
sweeps to deep-square leg.
sweeps once again square of the wicket on the onside to the deep.
chips it in the air wide of mid-on to the deep, fielder runs in from deep-midwicket to field the ball.
works to the onside to midwicket, a terrible throw to the keeper, they get an overthrow.
pushes through extra cover for a single.
cuts behind point to the deep for couple of runs.
defended on the front foot, the keeper collects the ball on the bounce and breaks the stumps.
down the wicket and punches to long off.
works it down the ground to long on.
works it through square leg to the deep.
pushes it down the ground to long on.
defended to the off side.
sweeps it in front of square leg to the fence. Younis Khan reaches out to the delivery.
sweeps once again this time behind square leg.
punches it down the ground to long on.
pushed down the ground to long off.
down the wicket and Younis Khan lofts it high and down the ground to long off fence.
driven with the full face off the bat down the ground to long on.
works it through midwicket for couple of runs.
punched down the ground to long on.
reverse sweeps to short thirdman.
sweeps to deep-square leg.
driven square of the wicket on the off side to the deep.
works to the onside.
driven down the ground to long on.
driven through cover to the sweeper for a single.
moves forward and drives down the ground to long on.
moves forward and drives along the ground straight to the fielder at extra cover.
pulls it through midwicket for a single.
full toss and Younis Khan mistimes to short fine leg.
plays to the fielder at midwicket.
reverse sweeps but cannot get his timing right, gets it square of the wicket on the off side to the deep, brings up his 50.
driven down the ground to long off.
good length delivery angled across, left alone through to Dhiman Ghosh.
moves forward and mistimes the shot to the off side.
cuts to the sweeper cover for a single.
plays square of the wicket on the off side for a single.
good shot from Butt, driven back to the bowler, Reza does well to stop it with his left leg.
drives through the off side to the sweeper cover for couple of runs.
plays it to deep-midwicket.
full toss driven wide of long on for couple of runs.
100 for Butt, punches it down the ground to long on. Raises his bat to the crowd. Thanks God for all the effort. Butt 100 comes up in 100 balls. This is his 6th century.
cut behind point to the deep for couple of runs.
driven down the ground to long on.
works it through the vacant midwicket for a single.
wonderful cut shot, down on his left knee and cuts well to the point boundary.
pushes to the off side.
plays to extra cover.
wonderfully played, deliberately opens the face off the bat and glides it down to thirdman.
good slower delivery and Younis Khan picks it late and defends to the off side.
full delivery driven down the ground to long off.
down the wicket and punches to long on, brings up the 150 runs partnership.
a fumble in the deep as Butt works it through the vacant midwicket.
punches down the ground to long on.
moves back and punches down the ground to long on.
well played, sweeps it nicely to the long leg boundary.
moves forward and punches down the ground to long off.
lovely shot from Butt, down on his left knee and drives it through the off side to extra cover fence.
driven down the ground to long off for a single.
yorker length delivery dug out to cover for a single.
slower delivery punched down the ground to deep-mid off.
hits it in the air just over Ashraful at extra cover to the fence.
another drive in the air down the ground to long off. That shot brings up the 200 for Pakistan in the 33 overs.
quicker delivery and Younis Khan gets an outside edge down to short thirdman.
good shot but well fielded at midwicket by Reza, they get a single.
fumble at point by Ashraful as Younis Khan cuts square of the wicket on the off side.
cuts to short thirdman and once again there is a fumble, this time it is shahadat Hossain.
driven to the off side.
moves back and works through midwicket for a single.
plays and misses outside the off stump.
wide outside the off stump, once again Younis Khan cuts and misses.
driven through cover to the deep for couple of runs. This now is the highest second wicket partnership against Bangladesh.
caught! Digs in a short delivery and Younis Khan mishits the pull in the air in front of square leg, Reza runs around from midwicket to take the catch.
works it through square leg to the deep for a single.
back of a length delivery and Yousuf works to the onside.
moves forward and pushes to the off side.
cut to deep-point for a single, fielded by Aftab.
moves back and punches through cover for a single.
hits it in the air over the bowler to the deep, not a well timed shot.
makes room and cuts to the sweeper cover for a single.
works it through the vacant midwicket to the deep for a single.
yorker squeezed out to the off side for a single.
pushes square of the wicket on the onside.
good shot, smashed in the air over extra cover to the fence.
short and wide outside the off stump, cuts hard past backward point to the fence.
nice shot, driven with the full face off the bat down the ground to long off. This now is Butt's highest score and also the highest score by any Pakistan batsman against Bangladesh.
short ball and Yousuf swivels it over backward square leg fence for maximum.

caught! Hits in the air down to wide long on, Shakib Al Hassan runs sideways and takes the catch but falls as he loses balance, keeps the ball in the palm. Referred to third umpire to check if the catch was taken cleanly and it is a clean catch, Butt has to go, well played.
sweeps and misses, Dhiman Ghosh collects the ball and whips off the bails, referred to the third umpire for a stumping, green light flashes as little part of Yousuf's shoe was in the crease.
plays it down the ground to long on, Yousuf comes back for the second run.
plays square of the wicket on the off side for a quick single.
pushes to the onside for a single.
moves forward and drives to extra cover.
punches to mid-on for a single.
mistimes the drive to the off side, Ashraful moves across from extra cover to field the ball.
slower delivery well picked up Yousuf, who flicks it high in the air, one bounce to the midwicket fence.
once again another slower delivery, gets the outside edge down to thirdman.
driven through cover to the sweeper for a single.
cut behind point to the deep for couple of runs.
arm ball and Malik plays forward, strikes the pad, appeal turned down, it was close one.
defended on the onside.
down the wicket and hits inside-out to deep-extra cover.
pushes through cover for a single.
down the wicket and drives down the ground to long off.
moves forward and drives down the ground to long off.
cut in the air down to thirdman for a single.
cuts and misses outside the off stump, loud appeal for a caught behind turned down, there was some sound.
moves inside the line and works through midwicket for couple of runs.
mistimes the shot to mid-on for a single.
caught! Fuller delivery and Yousuf looking to play through the onside, gets  a top-edge to midwicket and Razzak takes the catch.
cut hard behind point to the fence.
works it through the onside to the deep for a single.
moves back and works it through midwicket for a single.
moves back and punches to the off side.
works it down the ground to long on
played back to the bowler.
drags it short slightly and Afridi pulls it to deep-midwicket, not a well timed shot.
moves across the stumps and edges it past the keeper to thirdman.
caught! Afridi mishits high in the air to deep-mid off and Mortaza running in from long off takes a good catch.
chops into the ground through cover to the deep for a single.
a leading edge along the ground  to extra cover, Ashraful has a shy at the stumps, misses it.
low full toss driven to mid-on.
eases it down to thirdman, using the pace of the bowler.
pushes to wide long on for couple of runs.
moves back and pushes to the off side.
down the wicket and looking to defend, misses the bat and takes the pad.
moves back and punches to mid-off, not well timed.
reverse sweeps past short fine leg to the fence.
plays to the off side for a single.
wide outside the off stump and Misbah pushes square of the wicket on the off side, shy at the stumps,  strikes it, they get another run as the ball deflects away.
full toss played to deep-backward square leg for a single.
works to mid-on for a single.
hits in the air through the off side to the sweeper.
short ball pulled around to deep-backward square leg for a single.
works it to midwicket but straight to the fielder.
driven down the ground to long on, comes back quickly for the second run.
plays down the ground to wide long on for couple of runs.
moves forward and drives to mid-off.
good full delivery and Misbah pushes softly down the ground to long off, this is poor fielding as they complete the second run.
plays to short thirdman for a single.
mistimes the drive down the ground to long on, another couple of runs.
extra bounce and Misbah gets a leading edge to the off side as he blocks, Malik takes off for a run but Misbah stays on, Malik has to go back quickly.
plays it down to thirdman for a single, a poor throw from the deep gives away an extra run.
short ball pulled well to long leg fence, well put away.

fuller delivery worked behind square leg to the deep. Razzak picks up the ball and throws the ball to the keeper, who has a shy at the stumps at the bowlers end and nobody is backing up, they run 4 for the ball.
pushes to the off side for a quick single.
right in the block-hole, digs it out back to the bowler.
fires it down the leg side and it is too wide for Dhiman Ghosh to collect it, goes to the fence for wides, terrible delivery.
makes room and cuts behind point.
good shot this time, makes room and cuts hard through point to the fence.
moves back and turns it around to midwicket, coming back for the second run as the throw comes in, puts in a good dive.
makes room and looks to go big on the onside, gets a top-edge over the keeper to the left of short thirdman.
lovely shot, makes room and drives through extra cover to the fence.

stumped! Tosses it up in the air and Malik comes down the wicket and looks to go big through the off side, misses it and Dhiman Ghosh behind the wicket collects the ball and whips off the bails to stump Shoaib Malik.
caught! Fuller delivery and Misbah mishits it high in the air to square leg, Razzak runs in from midwicket, judges it well and settles under it to take the catch.
opens the face off the bat and runs it down to thirdman.
pushes square of the wicket to deep-point, Riaz coming back for a tight second run completes it as the throw was bit wide.
played to short fine leg for a single.
off the pad to the onside.
lbw! Full delivery angling in, Riaz moves across his stumps and looks to work it through the onside, misses it and the ball strikes the pad, loud appeal and given by umpire Nadeem Ghauri.
short down the leg side, pulls it well down to fine leg fence.
yorked him!, Right in the block-hole and Naumanullah was too late in coming down as the ball passes the bat to rattle the stumps.
playsit down to thirdman for couple of runs.
pushes to mid-off for a single.
keeps it full once again, hit in the air over cover to the sweeper for a single.
goes hard at a full delivery outside the off stump and gets a leading edge high in the air over extra cover outside the circle, comes back for the second run.

inn2.comm: nervy start for Tamim as he goes for the offdrive and gets a thick under edge which just falls short of first slip
superb delivery, pitches on the corridor outside off and has Tamim poking forward
this one was slightly wider but looked just as unplayable as Tamim leans onto another drive and misses
gets some solid wood behind this one as he gets back and defends
holds the length back outside off and this one kicks up a little more, he lets it go
pushes forward for the offdrive but ends up mistiming it to mid-off
pitches it short of a length and Junaid does well to get on top of the bounce and punch it to cover
sticks to the same length, he walks across and taps it down to cover
banged in short, Junaid hops on the backfoot and executes a pull off the meat of the bat past square leg, he swivels and controls the shot
another meaty punch but this was placed straight to backward point
tests him out with a bouncer this time and Junaid just manages to duck as the ball sails over him
hits a good length on off and middle, he gets back and punches to the offside
that was slightly overpitched outside off, he leans forward and cracks that past backward point, Umar Gul runs across from fine leg and cuts it off
fullish on offstump, he gets a good stride forward and defends
rocks back and plays a punchy drive which just beats the diving backward point, the timing has been good so far from these two
gets this one to nip back in, he shapes to drive straight but inside edges that one onto the pad
defended solidly back to the bowler, he offers the full face of the bat
fuller in length, he offers the full face of the bat again and solidly pushes it back to the bowler, good stuff
boundary opportunity there for him, the ball slides on the pads and he whips it a little too early, ends up mistiming it to square leg
holds the length back of off and middle, he gets behind the line and pushes it back to the bowler
gets across and once again shows how solid he is in defence, pushing it back to Gul
looked like an edge, or at least at first glance, he drives away from his body and Akmal and the slips go up, Gul doesn't appeal for some reason, the umpire is also unmoved
oversteps, he pushes that to the covers
Free Hit: he charges down the track and launches it straight down Malik's throat at mid-off, he flings it to the striker's end but he was safely in his crease, the running was circumspect there
tests him out with a bouncer, this one fizzes past him as he evades it
full outside off and pushed back firmly to Asif
shapes to drive straight but turns the face of the bat and gets an inside edge to mid-on
shuffles just a touch and tucks it off his wrists to naumanullah at midwicket, he stops it with his boot
gets back and taps it onto his boot
Asif pitches it up slightly wide outside the line of offstump, Junaid leans forward for the square drive but slices it uppishly straight to Butt at backward point

that's two in two! That one pitches on a good length outside the line of offstump and just comes in a little, Aftab shapes to whip that across the line but the ball strtikes him high on the pad, Steve Bucknor thinks about it for a long time and gives it out. Aftab looks a little stunned with the decision and shakes his head as he walks off
Gul bangs it in short and wide outside off, Tamim slashes and gets a thick top edge which sails over the slips
and the top order stutters again! Gul pitches it up outside off and gets it to move away, Tamim prods forward and half heartedly goes for the drive and only manages a thin outside edge to the keeper
edgy start there, it moves away after pitching on off and Shakib just opens the face of the bat and plays it with soft hands just wide of second slip
late movement again and this time Shakib is beaten for it
slightly shorter in length, he walks across and taps it with soft hands in front of extra cover
Ashraful just taps it softly in front of the covers and sets off in a flash, excellent running
good running again as he gets back and taps it softly in front of point and charges down the track
hits a good length outside off, he slices it towards cover

that was a beauty! That's why Asif is such a magician, maan! He pitches it on a good length bang in line of the offstump, Shakib is completely squared up, at first he shapes to whip it across the line, the ball comes on a lot quicker and the ball just shaves the top of offstump
he just opens the face of the bat and glides it down to third slip
pitches on off and middle, he tucks it wide of midwicket for a single
gets forward and softly taps it in front of cover and sets off
good running again as he pushes it with soft hands in front of cover and sets off
hits a good length on off and middle, he gets across and tucks it wide of square leg
just a little wide outside off and he slices this wide of point
they're pushing the singles here, pitches on off and middle, he gets across and clips this wide of midwicket
shapes to pull a short one but he's too early on the stroke as he ends up mistiming it towards square leg
fires in a quick yorker outside off, he tries to dig it out but the extra pace beats him
just a little too short, Ashraful reads the length early, gets on top of the bounce and pulls over square leg
fullish in length outside off, he pushes this off the full face of the bat to mid-off who's fielding fairly close

pitches just outside off and angles down the leg side, he pulls but the ball keeps a little low and strikes him on the pad, Asif belts out an optimistic appeal but Bucknor shakes his head, that wasn't hitting anything
punches it just wide of cover, the fielder intercepts it one handed
pitches on a good length outside off, he goes on the walk and pushes it to mid-off
short of a length on off and middle, he pulls this along the ground past square leg
full outside off and in the slot to drive, he lunges forward to cream that past mid-off but mistimes it instead
holds the length back outside the offstump, he leans forward and drives straight to cover
Gil dishes out a short one and the lack of pace allows Ashraful to pull with control along the turf past mid-on
full and swinging in a little late, he shapes to drive past mid-on but just closes the face of the bat at the point of contact and mistimes it to mid-on
Dropped: Mahmudullah gets forward to drive and gets a thick outside edge which goes low to Younis at second slip, he cups it too early and spills the catch
the ball follows Younis again but this time the edge goes on the first bounce to him
Ashraful gets down the track, goes for the ugly hoick across the line and mistimes it wide of square leg
pitches on a fullish length on off and middle, he tucks this to the on side
holds the length back slightly, he opens the face of the bat and slices it down to point
the slower ball slips out a little too early and turns into a low full toss, that's easy for Ashraful as he pushes it through the line softly and beats mid-off
the bouncer, he's beaten on the hook and Bucknor signals that as the one bouncer for the over
shuffles across his stumps and he works that off his hips to the on side
back of a length outside off, he plays a punchy drive to the covers
pitches on middle and leg, he gets across and whips it across the line to the on side
bangs it in short but misdirects it wide outside the legstump, he arches under that one
gets a big stride across his stumps to cover the line as he defends to mid-off
hits a good length outside off, he gets across and pushes that towards point
pushed in much quicker and lands on a full length, he gets across and taps it softly back to the bowler
holds the length back, he gets on top of the bounce and punches it to cover
flighted outside off, he gets forward and defends
goes for a mighty sweep but he gets a thick top edge which goes on the first bounce to fine leg
lunges forward and pushes back to the bowler
gets forward and pushes to midwicket
nice one Sir! He flights it on off and middle, he gets down for the slog sweep and scoops it over square leg, Umar Gul can't get to it
lunges forward and pushes this wide of point
wide outside off and he gets forward and uppishly drives this wide of extra cover

great reflexes! Afridi bowls this one on a good length outside off, he tries to cheekily dab it down to third man with the turn but the thick outside edge is snapped up brilliantly by Misbah at slip who follows the direction of the ball early and cups it with both hands while diving to his right
flights it slowly outside off, he gets forward and defends
gets forward for the drive  but the turn beats him
gets forward to drive but checks his stroke
this one comes on straight and Reza gets an inside edge onto his pads
gets it to swing away from the right-hander and he's lured onto the drive, he ends up missing it
slightly shorter outside off, it holds its line before reaching the keeper
solid shot, Riaz overpitches and he leans forward and times it sweetly past mid-off, hardly a sound from the crowd acknowledging that
gets back and defends back to the bowler
hits a good length on middle and leg, he turns his wrists and tucks it to fine leg
beaten this time, he leans forward to drive on the up but is squared up by the late movement, that wasnt too far from a thin edge
pushed outside off, he gets forward and defends
slides on the pads, he tucks it through the line to fine len
pushed in on the pads, he clips to midwicket
pitches on a good length outside off, he gets back and punches to cover
slides on the shins, he rolls his wrists and tucks this to fine leg
fires this one fuller, he gets a few paces down the track and digs it back to the bowler
back of a length on middle and leg, he gets across and clips it to fine leg

chopped on, that lands just back of a length on on offstump and comes back in, he appears to try and defend that but is too lazy on the shot and gets a thin inside edge which hits the base of the stumps
what was that? Riaz bangs it in short, Ghosh is very late in evading that bouncer and the ball clips his elbow and beats the keeper
another shortish delivery, this one comes on quick and catches Ghosh on the pads as he tries to whip it off
another one just shoots up off a good length and he just manages to fend it off his glove
shapes to cut but gets a thick inside edge and the ball rolls back to the bowler
slides on the pads, he works it to fine leg
big turn there, it kicks and turns square and beats him
pitches outside off, he defends close to the pads
half volley outside off, he covers the line well and caresses it past extra cover
flighted outside off, he defends
hits a good length on middle, he defends off his pads
pitches short of a length on middle and leg, he tucks it to the on side
hits a good length outside off, he gets back and pushes it to the offside
